Marketing Data Analyst’s role at Zeptolab is to help its products grow with the marketing team via data.

You will be a part of the analytics team and work very closely with the marketing team and product teams. Marketing is a huge part of Zeptolab success, and you will have an opportunity to affect it. You will work independently, building and testing hypotheses, digging through data to help the team to find a direction and make the best possible decisions.

