Amplitude analytics system + SQL DB + internal DB;
An analytics team with eight professionals with sustainable knowledge sharing process;
Working on unified analytical tools with the data science team and continuously improve data’s value;
Drive! (Hundreds of millions of people will witness the results of your decisions and ideas worldwide. This is the level of responsibility on our team’s shoulders, and we’re looking for someone as driven as we are);
